snippet.title: Realm of the Undead - Steam Next Fest Trailer
snippet.description:
Download Demo on Steam!

Realm of the Undead is a round-based 1-4 player co-op zombie FPS, where you survive endless rounds of zombies that get tougher every round. Unlock and upgrade gear between missions in the PlayerHub!
